<font color=#FFFF00>I heard Yoo-jin is your daughter.</font>

781
00:58:49,531 --> 00:58:50,531
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandfather...</font>

782
00:58:50,648 --> 00:58:54,038
<font color=#FFFF00>If Yoo-jin is your daughter, then
