789
00:59:19,554 --> 00:59:21,087
<font color=#FFFF00>Why didn't you tell me? Why?</font>

790
00:59:22,375 --> 00:59:23,375
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

791
00:59:24,164 --> 00:59:27,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Fortunately, I had brought
