812
01:00:46,139 --> 01:00:48,796
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if you won't be able to get
in touch with me, don't worry.</font>

813
01:00:48,821 --> 01:00:50,146
<font color=#FFFF00>No, Hee-dong!</font>

814
01:00:51,140 --> 01:00:54,352
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't find a woman like
