815
01:00:54,898 --> 01:00:58,432
<font color=#FFFF00>Shin-ae was very good to you.
She's very good to me, too.</font>

816
01:00:58,906 --> 01:01:01,593
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, look at this necklace.
Shin-ae bought it for me.</font>

817
01:01:02,382 --> 01:01:04,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee-dong, I can't live without Shin-ae.</font>

818
01:01:04,843 --> 01:01:09,374
<font color=#FFFF00>- If you divorce her, I'll bite my tongue and die!
