850
01:03:31,521 --> 01:03:36,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee-dong! Hee-dong! Hee-dong!</font>

851
01:03:36,591 --> 01:03:39,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee-dong! Hee-dong! Hee-dong!
Hee-dong! Hee-dong!</font>

852
01:03:42,818 --> 01:03:44,255
<font color=#FFFF00>How can this happen?</font>

853
01:03:46,301 --> 01:03:48,247
<font color=#FFFF00>How can this happen?</font>

854
01:03:49,419 --> 01:03:56,067
<font color=#FFFF00>How? How can this happen? What
