859
01:04:26,123 --> 01:04:27,123
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

860
01:04:27,794 --> 01:04:29,435
<font color=#FFFF00>About my granddaughter?</font>

861
01:04:35,677 --> 01:04:39,513
<font color=#FFFF00>This is a report of Ms. Park
