863
01:04:50,568 --> 01:04:51,568
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

864
01:04:51,593 --> 01:04:53,911
<font color=#FFFF00>Slush fund?</font>

865
01:04:55,365 --> 01:04:56,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Embezzlement?</font>

866
01:04:57,943 --> 01:04:59,477
<font color=#FFFF00>My granddaughter did those things?</font>

