01:05:03,521 --> 01:05:08,853
<font color=#FFFF00>Why is Shin-ae preparing a slush fund?
For what reason?</font>

868
01:05:10,224 --> 01:05:13,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Like Dae-hoon had said, is she
not my real granddaughter?</font>

869
01:05:14,786 --> 01:05:20,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you saying your mother called Shin-ae
an imposter because she has dementia?</font>

870
01:05:20,802 --> 01:05:23,105
<font color=#FFFF00>Or else, how would she say such a thing in</font>

871
