01:05:53,104 --> 01:05:56,330
<font color=#FFFF00>About Shin-ae's DNA test last time...</font>

878
01:05:56,518 --> 01:05:59,283
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you tell your wife about it?</font>

879
01:05:59,556 --> 01:06:03,069
<font color=#FFFF00>No. We had decided to keep
that between ourselves.</font>

880
01:06:03,940 --> 01:06:04,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you sure?</font>

881
01:06:05,385 --> 01:06:07,924
<font color=#FFFF00>You really didn't tell anyone?</font>

882
01:06:08,830 --> 01:06:09,830
