883
01:06:12,151 --> 01:06:14,642
<font color=#FFFF00>Dal-ho, come home at once.</font>

884
01:06:18,197 --> 01:06:19,313
<font color=#FFFF00>Something is wrong.</font>

885
01:06:26,080 --> 01:06:28,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, my. Mother, what's wrong?</font>

886
01:06:32,565 --> 01:06:34,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, what do you think you're doing?</font>

887
01:06:34,425 --> 01:06:35,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell me yourself.</font>

888
01:06:36,252 --> 01:06:39,158
<font color=#FFFF00>Is Yoo-jin your daughter?</font>

889
01:06:40,869 --> 01:06:44,702
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought this was about something else.
Are you like this because of that?</font>

890
01:06:45,197 --> 01:06:47,025
<font color=#FFFF00>You wicked wench! You dirty wench!</font>

891
01:06:47,221 --> 01:06:49,783
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you hide your
child and marry Hee-dong?</font>

892
01:06:50,017 --> 01:06:53,404
<font color=#FFFF00>You deserve to die! My kind
Hee-dong didn't know she was</font>

893
01:06:53,429 --> 01:06:56,994
<font color=#FFFF00>your real daughter. He hugged,
carried, and played with her!</font>

894
01:06:57,478 --> 01:07:01,424
<font color=#FFFF00>If I think of that, I won't be
able to rest in peace when I die!</font>

895
01:07:06,432 --> 01:07:08,924
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. Yoo-jin is my daughter.</font>

896
01:07:09,393 --> 01:07:12,209
<font color=#FFFF00>But that happened in the past
