903
01:07:36,584 --> 01:07:38,706
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the end for you!</font>

904
01:07:39,709 --> 01:07:41,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Do whatever you want!</font>

905
01:07:41,357 --> 01:07:44,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I'll go down by myself?
You'll go down with me!</font>

906
01:07:44,955 --> 01:07:47,329
<font color=#FFFF00>If I go under, do you think you'll be safe?</font>

907
01:07:47,962 --> 01:07:51,024
